<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Hawsn<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und zweyer <expan>knabe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        die er <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Zegentot,
                        empfremdt sol <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Nu ist uns <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> newlich <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, also <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir den
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Hawsn<ex>er</ex></expan> für uns besant und
                            <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit im <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        geredt, daz er <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> selb <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> sol. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefalle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>is</expan>
<expan>bap<ex>tis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>.</ab>
